race.comment: STAR EMPIRE (6) has gone to a new level this prep and closed strongly when second over 1600m at this track. Kissick retains the ride and expect to see another big performance. GOLD TRACKER (3) deep into the campaign and should get the right tempo from the low draw. Picked them up strongly been scoring over 1600m at this track on November 24. Will be tough to stop. ALBANIAN BEAUTY (10) kept fresh when shedding his Maiden status at start five over 1400m at this track. Should appreciate the mile and must be respected now that the penny has dropped. DIVINE CONCLUSION (2) back in class and trip after knocking up late when fifth over 1800m at Gundagai three weeks ago. Gets the 3kg claim and stays in the mix. KEITH (5) worked hard from the wide gate when a dismal last over this trip at Albury. Assess on the run two-back. Improver.
